This directory vendors an esp_lcd panel driver for the ST7735 / ST7735S LCD
controller.

Upstream:  Espressif Systems esp_lcd panel-vendor driver family
           (https://github.com/espressif/esp-bsp,
            https://components.espressif.com/ — esp_lcd_st7789 / esp_lcd_st7796
            reference drivers, which this ST7735 driver follows field-for-field)
License:   Apache License 2.0
Commit:    not pinned — adapted from the Espressif esp_lcd reference driver to
           drive the ST7735 controller used by SniffCheck's panel.

